OL,5, Documents showing Post Office top      
OL,6, bosses secretly decided in April 2014  
OL,7, to sack forensic accountants who had   
OL,8, found bugs in their IT system have been
OL,9, obtained by the BBC.                   
OL,11,FA Post Office board sub-committee,     
OL,12,Fcodenamed "Project Sparrow", took the  
OL,13,Fdecision with the full knowledge of the
OL,14,Fgovernment.                            
OL,16,FFormer sub-postmaster Alan Bates said  
OL,17,Fit was further proof of a "total       
OL,18,Fcover-up".                             
OL,20,FThe Post Office declined to comment.   
